Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:13.93,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}至少纵声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.18,0:22:25.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}恸哭和绝望之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:31.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}等待我们的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.78,0:22:38.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}都不过是生命梦想的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:41.42,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}为之奋斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.67,0:22:46.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}当下的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:53.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你哭泣的夜晚之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.14,0:22:59.19,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}藏有遥远未来的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:03.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}静谧在等待你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:10.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}耀眼的丘陵 必能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.24,0:23:15.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}你所在的地平线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.95,0:23:22.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur2}奏响你的心铃
